  <brief_title>Can Blood Glucose Levels During the Perioperative Period Identify a Population at Risk for Hyperglycemia?</brief_title>
  <official_title>Can Blood Glucose Levels During the Perioperative Period Identify a Population at Risk for Hyperglycemia</official_title>
  <sponsors>
